Sudoku version 0.01
=========================

Extensible Sudoku Puzzle and solver.  See pod documentation for more.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

SCRIPT

You can watch the solver work by running 

./sudoku.pl puzzles/test1.puz

or test2.puz, etc.  Be warned, solving Hex puzzles is quite slow right now.  sudoku.pl is not installed by make install.

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Moose
  

